      <sec id="article-18481.s10" sec-type="Prognosis">
        <title>Prognosis</title>
        <p>When bowel obstruction is managed promptly, the outcome is good. In general, when bowel obstruction is managed non surgically the recurrence rate is much higher than those treated surgically.</p>
      </sec>
