      <sec id="article-18481.s12" sec-type="Postoperative and Rehabilitation Care">
        <title>Postoperative and Rehabilitation Care</title>
        <p>The postoperative recovery, in most cases of bowel obstruction, is slow. These patients need prophylaxis against deep venous thrombosis and prevention of atelectasis. Ambulation is necessary. Time to feeding can vary depending on the ileus.</p>
      </sec>
